      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great in the driveway! I\u2019ve made sure to keep it clean and well-loved, so it's totally ready for its next adventure. It runs smoothly and is just waiting for a new owner to take the wheel. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
