    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential. The chassis is well-sorted, having undergone subframe reinforcement and a recent suspension overhaul with poly-bushings. Maintenance is current, including the essential VANOS service and valve clearance adjustments. While it shows the minor patina of a car that has been enjoyed, the mechanical components are robust, ensuring the tactile, analog feedback this platform is renowned for.",
