    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and fun weekend getaways. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it runs like a charm and still looks wonderful parked in the driveway! If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready for its next adventure, this is the one. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I'd love for it to go to a great new home!",
