    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 987.2-generation Porsche Cayman S. This mid-engine masterpiece is powered by the 3.4L 9A1 flat-six featuring Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), delivering linear power without the IMS concerns of earlier blocks. The 6-speed manual transaxle provides short, precise throws, while the hydraulic steering rack offers the tactile feedback modern electric systems lack. The chassis retains its composure via a well-sorted MacPherson strut arrangement, and the braking system features four-piston aluminum monobloc calipers over vented rotors for superior heat dissipation. Recent maintenance includes a high-pressure fuel pump inspection and a comprehensive cooling system pressure test. A purist\u2019s specification that excels in corner-exit traction and rotational balance.",
